    "A simple method involves feeding the video into a multimodal model [58]- [61] for video description.",
    "However, we observed a significant occurrence of hallucination in open-source models, as described in the Appendix.",
    "To address this issue, we adopted In-Context Learning and Chain-of-Thought [62] based on GPT-4V [63], [64] to generate captions in stages.",
    "Fig. 2b shows the detailed text generation and fusion process.",
    "During this process, we also used titles and hashtags as supplements to reduce model biases."
